Trade/Device Name(s): Atlas One Step hCG Urine Pregnancy Test (Strip)
Atlas One Step hCG Urine Pregnancy Test (Cassette)
Atlas One Step hCG Urine Pregnancy Test (Midstream)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Atlas One Step hCG Urine Pregnancy Test in strip, cassette, and midstream formats for early pregnancy detection
Indications for Use Summary: Visually-read, lateral flow immunoassay for qualitative detection of human chorionic gonadotropin (hCG) in urine to aid early detection of pregnancy; for over-the-counter single use only, confirmation required by clinical examination
